{"tid":2087172,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"習狗收皮啦 你咸家產都未開到我年啊傻閪","createTime":"2020-06-30T15:16:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:50:16.000Z","uid":234509,"like":152,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d176755f9ecb683f0e32e85dabfd3b222181d0","tid":2087172,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"未撚驚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習狗收皮啦 你咸家產都未開到我年啊傻閪<br />\n你係到谷撚住都冇撚用你啖氣忍到下世啦柒頭<br />\n我笠撚硬水 你今世都拉唔撚到我架啦<br />\n你買撚曬2047啲場啦傻閪<br />\n屌你老母立晒法<br />\n比人笑都好過比國安打到變豬頭啦傻閪<br />\n突然立法都知你兩手準備 日度夜度想拉我 你都戇撚鳩<br />\n正所謂 阿婆跑得快 一定有古怪<br />\n150%肯撚定習狗有準備嘅<br />\n咁突然立法 你當我傻？屌你老味<br />\n比你笑我笠水 你叻囉<br />\n雖然笠水啫 你當我傻架？叫個笠開水嘅企定定俾你拉 你老母生撚左你個腦未 屌你老母"},{"pid":"2bb778fc87fb89de36c8167c004a16ca4e980b05","tid":2087172,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"巴打勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9818e8899afb400aec4863d662c60f52736ee389","tid":2087172,"uid":35112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"樓上冇轉account???"},{"pid":"9e59e32e35e04ac53462a71729701485597baa7d","tid":2087172,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9818e8899afb400aec4863d662c60f52736ee389","tid":2087172,"uid":35112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"樓上冇轉account???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"咪屈用funson會俾人bam"},{"pid":"7199b6784c17fea7bebf93557021b5e6fdc32d27","tid":2087172,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"71c81c566b44f6ec826dad5647004321ca9085a7","tid":2087172,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:08:20