r />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"adbacefd013a5acce1e4e8959e8de167449f7ac7","tid":2087172,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f3e9ad46871a97ce8fb050c2b70eb2b63489416","tid":2087172,"uid":219225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"習清，恕我軟弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T20:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6a90901308aead0b0cbe9887144db06e8b1991","tid":2087172,"uid":317485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T21:03:02.000Z","msg":"恕我軟弱"},{"pid":"c3bbd0fca625e5bf122fdf4538b25d1790b828ec","tid":2087172,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"690f83c0f135dfa125fe27b2b5a5144adbb3e6e1","tid":2087172,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:34:09.000Z","msg":"有冇原po 想睇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"暖化撚又輸 濕凍好撚痴線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac71415f36d5d1eef8ba0a9bbd0079d1f6642fcb","tid":2087172,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb04e6335574294cf8004145fc1af7bdbe99f40e","tid":2087172,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T19:00:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住<br />\n樓主個po有抹黑成份同不實內容<br />\n我代樓主向習總道歉<br />\n已經寫咗email叫連仔del po"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:09:08.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"00bbcc78383ba39ec1df4c9e54876fff02f96c58","tid":2087172,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cbbf840144914b32fd9b434a52f797232a976b3","tid":2087172,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5375ead2d6b4491b994bbc97af9fc8c16828d610","tid